================================================================================
CONFIGURATION OPTIONS (for modding)
================================================================================

spawnRoomOpenWall values:
  0 = WEST  (left side open, default)
  1 = EAST  (right side open)
  2 = NORTH (top side open)
  3 = SOUTH (bottom side open)

To change spawn room size, edit GameConfig-default.json:
  "spawnRoomSize": 5        <- Change to 3, 4, 5, 6, etc.
  "spawnPointInRoomX": 2    <- Center index (spawnRoomSize / 2)
  "spawnPointInRoomY": 2    <- Center index (spawnRoomSize / 2)

